---
title: Chicken & Pepper Cavatappi Milano with Fresh Mozz, Crispy Panko & Chives
description: No matter the weather, it’s impossible not to daydream about a bubbly, soul-warming pasta dish. Well, folks, that dream is now a reality. This delicious dish has curly cavatappi and tender strips of roasted bell pepper cloaked in a creamy tomato-herb sauce. It’s topped off with fresh mozzarella and crispy panko before being broiled to gooey, golden-brown perfection. Yep, this one-pan wonder is guaranteed to satisfy all your carby cravings. (We’re all about making dreams come true.)
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/621faa2e98079c3d1f6a8af2-7dd6b4e3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-pepper-cavatappi-milano-621faa2e98079c3d1f6a8af2-c75818e7.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chicken-pepper-cavatappi-milano-621faa2e98079c3d1f6a8af2
servings: 2
cuisine: Italian
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
